src:
Vietato camminare a piedi: non si passa
01 Nov 2019, 15:30 by Segnalazione WhatsApp



Marciapiede impraticabile e auto in divieto di sosta. E dove si passa? Statale 114, incrocio Via Contesse
text:
It is forbidden to walk on foot: you cannot pass
01 Nov 2019, 15:30 by WhatsApp Reporting



Impassable pavement and cars not allowed to park. And where do you go? State Road 114, Via Contesse intersection
